show.title: The Dragon Returns to His Homeland
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/qTHD9R
show.description: They called him "The Dragon" – a force of nature driven from the land he once protected. Now, a desperate plea from his ravaged homeland ignites a burning resolve within him. Returning to a kingdom teetering on the brink of collapse, he finds his people oppressed and his family's legacy tarnished. With a path paved by brutal enemies and forgotten allies, The Dragon must unleash his dormant power and reclaim his rightful place, not just for vengeance, but to forge a new destiny for his shattered land.
